# Component Measurement Using Ultrasonic Sensor

## Publication
- International Research Journal of Engineering and Technology (IRJET)
- Volume 05, Issue 05
- May 2018

## Abstract
This paper presents the design and development of an instrument to measure
geometrical parameters such as length, width, and height of components using
an ultrasonic sensor. The system reduces manual effort, improves portability,
and provides accurate measurements using Arduino and LCD display integration.

## Keywords
- Ultrasonic Sensor
- Component Measurement
- Arduino
- Job Inspection
- Job Analysis

## Hardware Used
- Ultrasonic Sensor
- Arduino (ATmega328P)
- 16x2 LCD Display
- Acrylic Measurement Modules

